          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-1" n="1">Hither from <hi rend="underlined">Mexico</hi> I came,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-2" n="2">To serve a proud <hi rend="underlined">Hibernian</hi> Dame;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-3" n="3">Was long submitted to her Will,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-4" n="4">At length She lost Me at Quadrille:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-5" n="5">Thro' various Shapes I often pass'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-6" n="6">Still hoping to have Rest at last:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-7" n="7">And still ambitious to obtain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-8" n="8">Admittance to the Patriot Dean:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-9" n="9">And sometimes got within his Door,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-10" n="10"><note place="foot">·Alluding to the sums annually lent by the <hi rend="underlined">Dean</hi> to poor Tradesmen, without Intere\<hi rend="italics">rest of note concealed under the guard</hi>\.</note>But soon turned out to serve the Poor;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-11" n="11">Not stroling Idleness to Aid,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-12" n="12">But honest Industry decay'd:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-13" n="13">At length an Artist purchas'd Me;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-14" n="14">And wrought Me in the Shape you See.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-15" n="15">This done, to <hi rend="underlined">Hermes</hi> I apply'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-16" n="16">O <hi rend="underlined">Hermes</hi>, gratify my Pride;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-17" n="17">Be it my Fate to serve a Sage,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-18" n="18">The greatest Genius of his Age;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-19" n="19">That matchless Pen let Me supply,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-20" n="20">Whose living Lines shall never dye;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-21" n="21">I grant your Suit, the God replied;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-610-770L-line-22" n="22">And here he left Me to reside.</l>
          </lg>
